{"tid":1442424,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"呢張卡會唔會應驗呢？","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T20:30:59.000Z","uid":302248,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edfab26ed72f410567a1180e1a66d7d7cf1b5511","tid":1442424,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"自從五大訴求嘅有顏色版本出現之後，小弟即刻就諗起光明會卡片入面其中一張：綜合的災難<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGpUN6V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGpUN6V.jpg&h=aee7df59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXpamr4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXpamr4.jpg&h=a1fc8435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡片後面嘅鐘樓，可以係指緊尖沙咀嗰個，加上而家反送中運動開啟咗大量戰線，對於政府，黑警，愛國人仕而言係多種災難發生。<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"9004d1d7e3aac4a5f330bba76c9fa74e1244e110","tid":1442424,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01efe60697bde28b49f6939eedf56fd52a51a412","tid":1442424,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450356afe551febf14dfc2c8fa7dea970d1b3e41","tid":1442424,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b32d8dde8d9041882c17a0aea221ea1dbac1722","tid":1442424,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc12b2de5b15ccad4d8e285a6867de0a615a61be","tid":1442424,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"樓主改標題啦<br />\n改做文宣新方向之類"},{"pid":"efad97b5e63448058ffbe5195449705d2f7fda8a","tid":1442424,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:58:20.000Z"